items.name: Largemouth Bass
items.itemDescription: A carnivorous freshwater gamefish. Native to Northern America.

items.name: Carp
items.itemDescription: An Oily freshwater fish. Native to Europe and Asia.

items.name: Sunfish
items.itemDescription: Centrarchidae, a ray-finned freshwater fish. Native to Northern America.

items.name: Trout
items.itemDescription: A freshwater fish closely related to salmons.

items.name: Salmon
items.itemDescription: A ray-finned ocean fish. Native to the North Atlantic and Pacific Ocean.

items.name: Sturgeon
items.itemDescription: A kind of fish which gets harvested for their roe, which is processed into caviar. There are species native to rivers and species native to oceans.

items.name: Pacific Cod
items.itemDescription: A ray-finned fish native to the northern Pacific.

items.name: Mackerel
items.itemDescription: A type of fish, which are found in temperate and tropical seas and live coastal or offshore. They typically have vertical stripes on their back.

items.name: Swordfish
items.itemDescription: Large, highly migratory predatory fish, found in tropical and temperate parts of the Atlantic, Pacific and Indian Ocean.

items.name: Drift Bottle
items.itemDescription: A bottle which contains a letter.

items.name: One Ring
items.itemDescription: The One Ring is one of the most powerful artifacts ever created.

items.name: Salt
items.itemDescription: Used for food seasoning or as preservative.

items.name: Flour
items.itemDescription: A fine, powdery foodstuff, used chiefly in baking.

items.name: Butter
items.itemDescription: Butter is a dairy product made from the fat and protein components of milk or cream.

items.name: Lemon
items.itemDescription: A citrus fruit, sour, lemonade can be made from it.

items.name: Cabbage
items.itemDescription: A vegetable of the mustard family, with big green leaves.

items.name: Carrot
items.itemDescription: A biennial Eurasian plant of the parsley family.

items.name: Cigar
items.itemDescription: A compact roll of tobacco leaves prepared for smoking.

items.name: Scars Dagger
items.itemDescription: A knife, short enough to be concealed under clothes. Mead Scars weapon of choice.

items.name: Scars Belt
items.itemDescription: The leather belt worn by Mead Scars.

items.name: Food Bag
items.itemDescription: A lot of food can be carried in this bag, useful on long journeys.

items.name: Potion Bag
items.itemDescription: Add potions or other liquids into this canteen, useful when you need a quick swig during battle.

items.name: Cooked Chicken
items.itemDescription: Use: Restores 5000 health over 12 sec. A whole cooked chicken, surprisingly still warm.

items.name: Rusty Lockbox
items.itemDescription: A mysterious rusty box with unknown contents. On the side it has etched 'Property of T.D.'

items.name: Iron Key
items.itemDescription: An old, heavy key made out of iron... but what does it unlock?

items.name: Nan's Secret Veggie Soup Recipe
items.itemDescription: The note reads: 'Nan's secret vegetable soup recipe passed down from many generations, keep it safe!'

items.name: Nan's Secret Veggie Soup
items.itemDescription: Use: Restores 1040 health and 1000 mana over 6 sec. T.D's favourite soup, just like how Nan made it.

items.name: Onion
items.itemDescription: A bulbous plant, cultivated as vegetable.

items.name: Tomato
items.itemDescription: A widely cultivated red fruit of the nightshade family.

items.name: X-Large Bag
items.itemDescription: A extra large bag with 50 slots.

items.name: Iron Fragments
items.itemDescription: Use: Combine 5 Iron Fragments to create a single Iron Ore.

items.name: Coal Fragments
items.itemDescription: Use: Combine 10 Coal Fragments to create a single Coal.

items.name: Silver Fragments
items.itemDescription: Use: Combine 15 Silver Fragments to create a single Silver Ore.

items.name: Gold Fragments
items.itemDescription: Use: Combine 20 Gold Fragments to create a single Gold Ore.

items.name: Clam
items.itemDescription: Use: Open the clam to see what's inside.

items.name: Pearl
items.itemDescription: A perfectly round, glistening white pearl.

items.name: Million Dollar Cookie
items.itemDescription: A cookie made of solid gold with diamonds... do not try to consume it.

items.name: Crude Sickle
items.itemDescription: 30% chance to give a bonus harvest per Seed while Farming. Doesn't give additonal XP.

items.name: Steel Sickle
items.itemDescription: 45% chance to give a bonus harvest per Seed while Farming. Doesn't give additonal XP.

items.name: Unnamed Sickle
items.itemDescription: 60% chance to give a bonus harvest per Seed while Farming. Doesn't give additonal XP.

items.name: Crude Fishing Spear
items.itemDescription: 30% chance for double drop while Fishing. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary items.

items.name: Bone Fishing Spear
items.itemDescription: 45% chance for double drop while Fishing. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary items.

items.name: Fine Bone Fishing Spear
items.itemDescription: 60% chance for double drop while Fishing. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary items.

items.name: Lucky Shell
items.itemDescription: 50% increased chance for Uncommon, Rare and Epic items while Fishing.

items.name: Fishermans Hat
items.itemDescription: 50% decreased chance for Junk while Fishing. Improve the accuracy of catching fish by keeping the sun out of your eyes.

items.name: Crude Mining Hammer
items.itemDescription: 30% chance for double drop while Mining. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary drops.

items.name: Steel Mining Hammer
items.itemDescription: 45% chance for double drop while Mining. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary drops.

items.name: Fine Steel Mining Hammer
items.itemDescription: 60% chance for double drop while Mining. Doesn't give additonal XP and excludes Rare, Epic and Legendary drops.

items.name: Lucky Rock
items.itemDescription: 50% increased chance for Uncommon, Rare and Epic drops while Mining. It's more than just a rock... this rock brings luck to anyone who holds it.

items.name: Oil Lantern
items.itemDescription: 50% increased chance for Ores while Mining. Improves your visibility in the dark while mining.

items.name: Note
items.itemDescription: You have been led astray by another adventurer... you will not find the secrets of the moon here, she who lays in the Troubled Cove holds all the answers.

items.name: Slime Cookie
items.itemDescription: A delicious looking cookie, covered in slime.

warriorAbilities.name: Deep Slash
warriorAbilities.abilityDescription: Slash deep into the target causing 150% Physical damage on your next hit.\n\n8 sec cooldown.

warriorAbilities.name: Battle Cry
warriorAbilities.abilityDescription: Cry out during battle, increasing your Physical damage by 50% over 10 sec.\n\n30 sec cooldown.

warriorAbilities.name: Shoulder Ram
warriorAbilities.abilityDescription: Shoulder rams the target, causing their attack speed to be slowed by 50% over 8 sec.\n\n15 sec cooldown.

warriorAbilities.name: Body Slam
warriorAbilities.abilityDescription: Body slams the target, stunning them for 3 sec.\n\n15 sec cooldown.

warriorAbilities.name: Maim
warriorAbilities.abilityDescription: Maims the target, causing 200% Physical damage over 8 sec.\n\n20 sec cooldown.
